snippet.title: Bad Apple!! [Electro Swing Remix (ft. OR3O & adrisaurus)] (English/Japanese)
snippet.description:
Yooo! It's finally here. We've been wanting to upload this for a while now. I'm so happy with this project. It's my first time making a Touhou remix and first remix that has Japanese in it. Big thanks to OR3O and adrisaurus for the awesome vocals. Please check their channels out! Also, watch out for the music video of this song on OR3O's channel.

OR3O: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTAyRNwgMv_vvM8Z9UvKKEg
adrisaurus: https://www.youtube.com/user/adrisaurus

Amazing artwork by: https://twitter.com/Burfabutt

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 

MUSIC VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EYXR5DT2IbY
iTunes/Spotify: https://spoti.fi/30HjyNo
Instrumental version: https://youtu.be/VJx2d40kT78

Free download/Listen on Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/the-musical-ghost/bad-apple-electro-swing-ft-or3o-adrisaurus

Tempo: 128 BPM
Genre: Electro Swing

Sample used: Sidney Bechet - Polka Dot Rag
